Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(华沙 1939年)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-是席皮尔曼先生吗 -你好\N{\rEng}- Mr. Szpilman? - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是特地来拜访您的 我很喜欢您的演奏\N{\rEng}I came specially to meet you.I love your playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫多萝塔 我是裘瑞克的妹妹\N{\rEng}My name's Dorota, I am Jurek's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,您流血了\N{\rEng}You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 多萝塔\N{\rEng}Come Dorota
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过些时日你大可写爱慕信给他 但现在时机不对\N{\rEng}You can write him a fan letter later.This isn't the best time. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,裘瑞克 你过去都把她藏在哪里的\N{\rEng}Jurek, where have you been hiding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道要带什么 -你老是带太多东西\N{\rEng}- I don't know what to take. - You always take too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带几只提箱\N{\rEng}How many suitcases are you taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 我要带上西蒙叔父的肖像画吗\N{\rEng}What do you think, should I take uncle Szymon's portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,带不带随便你 你自己决定\N{\rEng}Take it, don't take it,take what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我急出病来了吗\N{\rEng}Can't you see I'm worried sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他就要回家了 他会没事的\N{\rEng}He'll come home, he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你有另一只和这个一样的箱子\N{\rEng}You should have another case just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 瓦列迪克回家了\N{\rEng}Mama, Wladek is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢老天 瓦列迪克\N{\rEng}Thank God. Wladek!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-你受伤了吗 -一点小伤 不要紧的\N{\rEng}- You're wounded? - No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我都忧虑成疾了\N{\rEng}I've been worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过她不用担心 你要随身带着证件\N{\rEng}I told her not to worry.You had your papers on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你被炸到的话 他们就晓得该把你送到哪儿去\N{\rEng}If you'd been hit by a bomb,they'd know where to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亨瑞 别...别说那种话 愿上帝宽恕你\N{\rEng}Henryk, don't say things like that.God forbid. God forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 瓦列迪克回来了\N{\rEng}Papa, Wladek is home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么跟你说的 你在做什么\N{\rEng}What did I tell you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁看见我的宽边帽\N{\rEng}Is anybody see my hat with the wide brim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在进行轰炸 广播关闭了\N{\rEng}They've bombed us. We're off the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙不是唯一的广播站\N{\rEng}Warsaw is not the only radio station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾行李 亲爱的 把你的东西打包好\N{\rEng}Pack, darling.Get your things packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要到哪里去\N{\rEng}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-离开华沙 -离开华沙去哪里\N{\rEng}- Out of Warsaw. - Out of Warsaw where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没听说吗\N{\rEng}You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听说什么\N{\rEng}Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看见报纸吗\N{\rEng}Haven't you seen the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,报纸在哪里\N{\rEng}Where's the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿来包东西了\N{\rEng}I used it for packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-她把报纸拿来包东西 -政府已经迁到陆柏林了\N{\rEng}- She used it for packing. - The government has moved to Lublin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以四肢健全的男人都必须离开这座城市\N{\rEng}22All able-body men must leave the city, go across the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为了建立一道新的防御线\N{\rEng}set up a new line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,除了女人 没人还留在这栋房子里\N{\rEng}There isn't anybody left to the building, only the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,男人都已经离开了\N{\rEng}The men have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人去建立新防御线 你打算做什么\N{\rEng}What do you think you'll do while they set up a new line of defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拖着你的箱子到处游荡吗\N{\rEng}Wonder around with your suitcases?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾一下 瓦列 没时间了\N{\rEng}Pack, Wladek. There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪儿都不去\N{\rEng}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我也不要离开\N{\rEng}Good. I'm not going anywhere either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡闹了 我们必须在一起\N{\rEng}Don't be ridiculous,we've got to keep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 如果要死的话 \N{\rEng}Look. If I'm going to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿死在自己家里 我不走\N{\rEng}I prefer to die in my own home, staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝宽恕你\N{\rEng}God forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵了 电台有重要消息 听\N{\rEng}Shut up, I've got something. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,据BBC报导\N{\rEng}...from the BBC in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,英国政府尚未得到任何...\N{\rEng}The British government having received no reply...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对德国政府发出的最后通牒的回复\N{\rEng}to the observations presented to the German government...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,正式向纳粹德国宣战\N{\rEng}has declared war on nazi Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-太棒了 太棒了 -预计...\N{\rEng}- That's wonderful! Wonderful! - It is expected that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...在数小时内\N{\rEng}...within the next few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,法国将发布同样的声明\N{\rEng}France will make a similar declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,波兰将不再孤立无援\N{\rEng}Poland is no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 太棒了\N{\rEng}Wonderful, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 这真是一顿美妙的晚餐\N{\rEng}Mama, that was a great dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}It certainly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,每当有值得庆贺的事情 你需在饭菜上花心思\N{\rEng}When there's something to celebrate,you've got to make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为大不列颠和法国举杯\N{\rEng}Here's to Great Britain and France!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说吧\N{\rEng}I told you? Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会没事\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,5,003块\N{\rEng}Five thousand and three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,全部就这些吗\N{\rEng}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,5,003波币 我们就剩下这些了\N{\rEng}Five thousand and three zlotys, all we've got left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还超出3,003元\N{\rEng}It's 3,003 zlotys too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 最新流动资产限额条例\N{\rEng}Look."Further restrictions regarding liquid assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人在家中放置现金上限为2,000波币\N{\rEng}Jews will be allowed to keep a maximum of 2,000 zlotys at home. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的钱该怎么处理呢\N{\rEng}What do we do with the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把它存进银行里 帐户会被冻结\N{\rEng}Deposit it in a bank. a blocked account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,银行 谁会笨到把钱存进德国人的银行里\N{\rEng}Banks! Who'd be stupid enough to deposit money in a German bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以把钱藏起来\N{\rEng}We could hide the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看这里 我们可以把钱藏在花盆下面\N{\rEng}Look here.We can hide the money under the flowerpots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我们要采取通过通过实践考验的办法\N{\rEng}no no no, I'll tell you what we'll do.We'll use tried and tested methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我们上一次是怎么做的吗\N{\rEng}You know what we did in the last war?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在桌脚凿了个洞 把钱藏进去\N{\rEng}We made a hole in the table leg,and hid the money in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他们把桌子扛走呢\N{\rEng}and suppose they take the table away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把桌子扛走是什么意思\N{\rEng}What do you mean take the table away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人会闯进犹太人家里夺取任何他们想要的东西\N{\rEng}the Germans go into Jewish homes and they just take anything they want
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,家具 值钱的物品 任何东西\N{\rEng}furniture, valuables, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,会吗\N{\rEng}Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 他们怎可能会要这样一张桌子\N{\rEng}idiot, Why'd they want to take a table like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么\N{\rEng}What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\rEng}Listen. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最理想的地方\N{\rEng}This is the best place for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会想到要搜查花盆\N{\rEng}No-one would think of looking under the flowerpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 听我说 我已经想过了\N{\rEng}No, listen. I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗 这想法倒与众不同 -我们该怎么做\N{\rEng}- Really? That's a change. - You know what we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要运用心理学\N{\rEng}We use psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,运用什么\N{\rEng}We use what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把钱和表放在桌上\N{\rEng}We leave the money and the watch on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后像这样把它们遮住\N{\rEng}and we cover them like this. In full view.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是傻瓜吗\N{\rEng}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人会到处搜索别的地方\N{\rEng}The Germans will search high and low and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证他们不会发现这个\N{\rEng} I promised that they never notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最愚蠢的事情\N{\rEng}That's the stupidest thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们当然会发现 瞧着\N{\rEng}Of course they'll notice. Look.Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜\N{\rEng}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我是傻瓜\N{\rEng}And you call me stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那方法很好 那是最不容易被...\N{\rEng}that's very good. because that's the last place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这得花多长时间把钱塞进去啊\N{\rEng}This would take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们又不赶时间 -那用不了多久\N{\rEng}- We're not in a hurry. - It won't take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 那你要怎么把钱拿出来\N{\rEng}How will you get them out? Tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-一张张扯出来吗 -听我说\N{\rEng}- You reach them out individually. - No-one listens to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 拜托有点秩序\N{\rEng}Quiet, order, order, please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她是律师 她喜欢秩序\N{\rEng}The lawyer, she likes order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\rEng}Listen, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把表放在花盆下 然后把钱塞进小提琴里\N{\rEng}Look.The watch we put under the flowerpot and the money we stuff in the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我还能弹奏吗\N{\rEng}But I'll still be able to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 会有办法的\N{\rEng}You'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,裘瑞克 我是瓦列·席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Jurek? It's Wladek Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\rEng}Wladek, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很好 谢谢 你呢\N{\rEng}fine, We're fine, thank you.And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种局势下还算不错\N{\rEng}Fine, under the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你为什么打电话 我们实在无能为力\N{\rEng}I guess I know why you're calling. There's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,电台不会恢复\N{\rEng}They won't reopen the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道 但是裘瑞克...\N{\rEng}Yes, I know, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有音乐 没有波兰人听的广播 什么都没有 \N{\rEng}No music, nothing,no radios for the Polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但我确信像你这样的钢琴家\N{\rEng}But sure you'll find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,会找到工作的\N{\rEng}A pianist like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧 但是...\N{\rEng}Maybe, maybe not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我无意冒犯\N{\rEng}listen,don't be offended,but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我打电话来不是为了讨论我以后的工作\N{\rEng}didn't call to discuss my future carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我对裘瑞克唠叨了好几个礼拜\N{\rEng}I nagged Jurek for weeks and weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最后他投降了 说 \N{\rEng}and at last he gave in and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"好吧 明天和我一起去电台"\N{\rEng}"All right, come with me tomorrow",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我来了 但他们把电台炸毁了\N{\rEng}so I came and...they bombed the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能与你那样认识很不错\N{\rEng}Meeting you like that was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的吗 -是的 这...让人记忆深刻\N{\rEng}- Really? - Yes, it was unforgettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很喜欢您的演奏 席皮尔曼先生\N{\rEng}I alwys love your playing, Mr. Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫我瓦列\N{\rEng}Call me Wladek, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能像你这样演奏萧邦的曲目\N{\rEng}No-one plays Chopin like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望那是个赞美\N{\rEng}I hope it's a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然是这个意思\N{\rEng}Of course, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...开个玩笑\N{\rEng}I was... trying to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意跟我去帕拉迪索喝杯咖啡吗\N{\rEng}Should we go Pradiso and have a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意之至\N{\rEng}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 你是做什么的\N{\rEng}And you, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚从音乐学校毕业\N{\rEng}I finished with the conservatoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是乐师\N{\rEng}You're a musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 只是...\N{\rEng}Yes. But only just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哪样乐器...抱歉 哪样乐器\N{\rEng}What instrument? I'am sorry,What instrument?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大提琴\N{\rEng}The cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢看女士演奏大提琴\N{\rEng}I love to see women playing the cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（禁止犹太人进入）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无礼 他们怎能这样\N{\rEng}This is disgraceful.How dare they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,人就是这样 他们比希特勒还希特勒\N{\rEng}You know what people are like, they want to be better nazis than Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要去抗议 -算了\N{\rEng}- I'm going in there to complain. - No
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,最好不要 相信我\N{\rEng}It's better not, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说太屈辱了\N{\rEng}It's so humiliating. Someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去别处吧\N{\rEng}find somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以到公园散步\N{\rEng}We can walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行 官方有令 犹太人禁止进入公园\N{\rEng}No, we can't.Official decree.No Jews allowed in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你是开玩笑吗\N{\rEng}My God. Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有开玩笑 是真的\N{\rEng}I'm not joking, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们可以坐在长椅上\N{\rEng}I suggest we could sit in a bench,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但官方另有禁令 "犹太人禁止坐在公共长椅上"\N{\rEng}but another official decree "no Jews allowed on public benches".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是荒谬\N{\rEng}This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我们可以做什么吧 我们只能站在这里交谈\N{\rEng}I tell what we can do,We can just stand here and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这是被允许的 不是吗\N{\rEng}and I think we're allowed to do that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你拉大提琴的 多萝塔 好极了\N{\rEng}So, you play the cello. Dorota, That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你最欣赏的作曲家是谁\N{\rEng}And who's your favorite composer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,萧邦 是吗\N{\rEng}Chopin? Really? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你得学他的大提琴奏鸣曲 不是吗\N{\rEng}you'll have to learn to play his cello sonata, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你呢 瓦列\N{\rEng}What about you, Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以为你伴奏 我弹钢琴 你拉大提琴\N{\rEng}Perhaps I could accompany.Me on the piano, you on the cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,席皮尔曼先生 你真是太棒太棒了\N{\rEng}Mr. Szpilman, you're quite,quite wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫我瓦列\N{\rEng}Call me Wladek, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙特区的犹太人 需配带标志\N{\rEng}"Free emblems for Jews in the Warsaw district.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在此下令 华沙特区所有的犹太人...\N{\rEng}I hereby order that all Jews in the Warsaw district...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,出门需配带醒目的标志\N{\rEng}will wear visible emblems when out of doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,此令自1939年12月1日起强制执行\N{\rEng}This decree will come into force on the first of December, 1939...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,适用于12岁以上的犹太人\N{\rEng}and applies to all Jews over 12 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,标志需配带于右臂\N{\rEng}The emblem will be worn on the right sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在白底绣上一颗蓝色的大卫王之星\N{\rEng}and will represent the blue star of David on a white background.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,底布必须要够大\N{\rEng}The background must be sufficiently large...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为星星的顶点间距离要8厘米\N{\rEng}for the star to measure eight centimeters from point to point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,线条的宽度必须为1厘米\N{\rEng}The width of the arms of the star must be one centimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,未遵从此令的犹太人将受严厉惩罚\N{\rEng}The Jews that do not respect this decree will be severely punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙特区首长\N{\rEng}Governor of the Warsaw district,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,费沙博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Fischer. "
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会戴\N{\rEng}I won't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会戴 我不要被贴上标签\N{\rEng}I won't wear it.I'm not going to be branded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\rEng}Let me see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是否意味着我们得自行准备这些臂章\N{\rEng}Does it say that we have to provid these armbands ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上哪儿去找\N{\rEng}Where will we get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不用去找 我们不会戴\N{\rEng}we won't to get them. We're not going to wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么没有鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请原凉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准走人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这个了吗\N{\rEng}Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 我正在工作 什么事儿\N{\rEng}What? What? I'm working. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们将要安置我们的地方\N{\rEng}It's where they're going to put us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你说"安置我们"是什么意思\N{\rEng}What do you mean "put us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙特区首长费沙博士\N{\rEng}"By order of the governor of the Warsaw district, Dr. Fischer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,关于在华沙建立犹太人隔离区的命令\N{\rEng}concerning the establishment of the Jewish district in Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人隔离区即将建成 所有犹太人...\N{\rEng}There'll be created a Jewish district in which all Jews
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙本地人或外地人 都必须进驻\N{\rEng}living in Warsaw or moving to Warsa will have to reside. "
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看这里\N{\rEng}Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,居住在指定区之外的犹太人\N{\rEng}"Jews living outside of the prescribed area...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,必须在1940年10月31日前迁至隔离区\N{\rEng}will have to move to the Jewish district by 31 of October, 1940."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿不可能把我们全部装下\N{\rEng}They won't get all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那里太小了 华沙有40万犹太人\N{\rEng}It's too small.There's 400 thousand of us in Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 36万人 这样便有可能\N{\rEng}No, 360 thousand.So it will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办\N{\rEng}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我现在该怎么办\N{\rEng}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEng}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 这是什么\N{\rEng}Mama, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就剩下这些了 20波币\N{\rEng}That's all we have left, 20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,20波币可以拿来买什么\N{\rEng}What can I buy with 20 zlotys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了一直吃马铃薯 马铃薯 马铃薯\N{\rEng}I'm sick of cooking potatoes,potatoes, potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就这个价格 这是我的出价\N{\rEng}That's the price.That's what I'm offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你接受 没人会出更高的价\N{\rEng}My advice is to accept.You won't get more from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,李帕先生 但这可是贝西斯坦牌的\N{\rEng}it's a Bechstein! Mr.Lipa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000元...我建议你收下吧\N{\rEng}2 thousand. My advice is to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿肚子的时候怎么办 啃钢琴吗\N{\rEng}What are you going to do when you're hungry? Eat the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-滚出去 你这龌龊卑鄙的家伙 -你是怎么回事\N{\rEng}- Get out! - What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们宁愿把它丢掉 滚\N{\rEng}We'd rather give it away. go on,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天还没吃过东西吧\N{\rEng}Haven't you eaten today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你在挣扎什么\N{\rEng}What are you suffering from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是疯狂\N{\rEng}You people are crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在帮你 2,000元 而且运费由我来付\N{\rEng}I'm doing you a favor. Two thousand and I'm paying for the removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不算运费\N{\rEng}I'm not even charging for the removal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天还没有吃东西\N{\rEng}You haven't eaten today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了\N{\rEng}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拿走吧\N{\rEng}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（1940年10月31日）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝塔\N{\rEng}Dorota
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hello. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本没有要来\N{\rEng}I didn't want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想看见这一幕 但是我...我控制不了自己\N{\rEng}I didn't want to see all this, but...I couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你近来好吗\N{\rEng}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不尽然\N{\rEng}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我表哥被逮捕了\N{\rEng}They arrested my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,裘瑞克说他们会释放他的\N{\rEng}Jurek says they'll let him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不幸\N{\rEng}This is disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不会太久的 别担心\N{\rEng}It won't last long. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我对自己也是这么说的\N{\rEng}That's what I said myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太荒谬了\N{\rEng}It's too absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我该走了\N{\rEng}I... I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,后会有期...\N{\rEng}Well, I'll see you...soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\rEng}Well...to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我原以为情况会更糟\N{\rEng}I thought it would be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要睡在哪里\N{\rEng}Where will we sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我和女孩儿们睡厨房\N{\rEng}I sleep in the kitchen with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你和亨瑞还有爸爸睡这里\N{\rEng}You, Henryk and papa, in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEng}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,过来看啊\N{\rEng}Come and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\rEng}Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,走开 走开\N{\rEng}Go away! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,卖出什么了吗\N{\rEng}Sell anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就卖出一本杜思妥也夫斯基的"白痴"\N{\rEng}just one,Dostoyevsky's "Idiot"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,3元波币\N{\rEng}3 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不过比昨天好\N{\rEng}Better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3枚肮脏的波币\N{\rEng}Three lousy zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但有人却大把大把的赚钞票\N{\rEng}And there are people there making millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不知道呢\N{\rEng}You don't know, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们贿赂警卫 警卫于是睁一只眼闭一只眼\N{\rEng}They bribe the guards,the guards turn a blind eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大量输入食物 烟酒 法国化妆品\N{\rEng}They bring cartloads of food,tobacco, liquor, French cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,穷人在他们周围死去 他们连痰也没啐一口\N{\rEng}And the poor are dying all around and they don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 请问你看见我丈夫伊沙克·沙曼了吗\N{\rEng}Excuse me, have you seen my husband, Izaak Szerman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一个高大英俊的男人 他蓄着灰色的胡子\N{\rEng}A tall handsome man,with a little gray beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有吗 -恐怕没有\N{\rEng}- No? - I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 祝好梦\N{\rEng}Good-bye.Sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果看见他 请写信给我好吗\N{\rEng}But if you see him, write to me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,伊沙克·沙曼\N{\rEng}Izaak Szerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得要有一条非犹太人的街道穿过我们的地方\N{\rEng}Why do we have to have a gentile street running through our area?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他们不绕过去\N{\rEng}Why can't they go around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 他们就要建一座桥了 你没听说吗\N{\rEng}Don't worry about it. They're about to build a bridge. Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一座桥? 一个笑话\N{\rEng}A bridge! A bridge!Those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人声称他们智商高\N{\rEng}The Germans claim to be intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么想吗 他们根本是不折不扣的白痴\N{\rEng}But do you know what I think?I think they're totally stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有家人要养\N{\rEng}I have a family to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,却得在这里花上半辈子时间等他们放行\N{\rEng}I spend half of my time here...waiting for them to let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为我来这里干嘛 来听音乐的吗\N{\rEng}Maybe they think I come here to listen to the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-说什么呢 你很急? -你有意见?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-找点乐子 -对 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你去跟他一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开 空出地方让这些犹太佬跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你 还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,继续跳 跳快点 继续 犹太佬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,继续跳 跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们回来了\N{\rEng}Good, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎克·海勒正在等你们\N{\rEng}Itzak Heller has been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-有什么事吗 -坐下来 请喝茶\N{\rEng}- What's this about? - Sit down, have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等姑娘们回来我再开饭\N{\rEng}I'll start lunch when the girls get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么\N{\rEng}So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他带饼干来\N{\rEng}He brought cakes, he is up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸做珠宝生意回来 他干得不错 是吧\N{\rEng}His father is back in the jewellery business,doing well him.eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人惊奇 珠宝\N{\rEng}Amazing, jewellery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在招人\N{\rEng}We're recruiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在招人\N{\rEng}Who is recruiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别耍小聪明 我是以朋友的身份来这里\N{\rEng}Don't be clever with me. I'm coming as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全国各地的犹太人涌进城市\N{\rEng}They're bringing Jews in from all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很快隔离区会有50万人 \N{\rEng}Soon there will be half million people in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更多的犹太人警察\N{\rEng}We need more Jewish police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的犹太人警察\N{\rEng}More Jewish police!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要我用警棍打那些反抗盖世太保的犹太人?\N{\rEng}you mean you want me to beat up Jews in my truncheon and catch the Gestapo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要有人做这件事 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Someone has got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么是我\N{\rEng}But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你只征召富家子弟\N{\rEng}I thought you only recruited boys with rich fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我父亲 看看我们 我的意思是...\N{\rEng}Look at my father, look at us...I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我在看 这就是为什么我在这里\N{\rEng}I'm looking at you, that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全家可以过好一点的生活\N{\rEng}Your whole family can have a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你要继续靠卖书维持生存 苟延残喘吗\N{\rEng}You want to struggling survive for selling the books in the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,正是如此\N{\rEng}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在帮你们\N{\rEng}I'm doing you people a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你呢 瓦列\N{\rEng}What about you,Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是位了不起的钢琴家 而我们有很棒的警察爵士乐团\N{\rEng}You're a great pianist.We've got a police jazz band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会展开双臂欢迎你加入我们 加入我们吧\N{\rEng}They'd welcome you with open arms.Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有工作\N{\rEng}You've got no work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我有工作\N{\rEng}Thank you, I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 当然\N{\rEng}right,yes it is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 瓦列 他要你停止演奏\N{\rEng}I'm sorry,Wladek.he wants you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁要我停止\N{\rEng}Who wants me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是说 看好的那一面\N{\rEng}I always say, look on the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在小小的隔离区里 你是知识分子 专业人士\N{\rEng}You're in a small ghetto with intellectuals, professional people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我们都更优秀\N{\rEng}You're better off than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这巨大的隔离区是个烂泥坑\N{\rEng}Here in the large ghetto it's a cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,朱哈达 给我点事情做吧\N{\rEng}You have to give me something to done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是位艺术家 鼓舞人们的灵魂\N{\rEng}You're an artist Wladek, you keep peoples' spirits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得够多了\N{\rEng}You do enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想帮忙 我想做点什么\N{\rEng}I want to help, I want to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你太出名了 伙计\N{\rEng}You're too well known.buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\rEng}you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们音乐家不是优秀的谋略者\N{\rEng}You musicians don't make good conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你太...太音乐了\N{\rEng}You're too... too musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是谁 -辛契·梅耶克\N{\rEng}- Who is that? - Symche.Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,传单满天飞 这城市要清除不受欢迎的人\N{\rEng}There are notices going up. City is to be cleansed of the undesirables.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.75,0:24:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-总是有传单满天飞 -你好 辛契\N{\rEng}- There's always notices going up. - Hello, Symche.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 多列克 您好 吉丝凯女士\N{\rEng}Dyrek. Mrs. Ysken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,裘哈达 工作忙吗\N{\rEng}Jehuda, working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,梅耶克 这位是波兰最伟大的钢琴家\N{\rEng}Majorek, This is the greatest pianist in Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.83,0:24:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或许也是全世界最棒的\N{\rEng}Maybe the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列迪斯洛·席皮尔曼 见见梅耶克\N{\rEng}Wladyslaw Szpilman, meet Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 -久仰大名\N{\rEng}- How do you do? - I know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.17,0:24:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但未曾听过您演奏\N{\rEng}I've never heard you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,梅耶克一直都在军中 是个出色的男人\N{\rEng}Majorek used to be in the Army.Brilliant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.65,0:24:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一不喜欢的就是 他不是个社会主义者\N{\rEng}The only thing I've got against him is he's not a socialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.58,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好现在离开 瓦列 宵禁时间快到了\N{\rEng}You better go now, Wladek. It's nearly curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们印了几份报纸吗\N{\rEng}You know how many copies we print of our newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,500份\N{\rEng}Five hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道一份报纸平均有几个人传阅吗?\N{\rEng}You know how many people on average read one copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:24:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,20人\N{\rEng}Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.93,0:25:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,总共有一万名读者\N{\rEng}That makes 10 thousand readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这些将为反动催生\N{\rEng}This will start the uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,梅耶克把它们藏进内裤 然后留在厕所里\N{\rEng}Majorek hides them in his underpants and leaves them in toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.01,0:25:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,厕所\N{\rEng}Toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.84,0:25:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我找得到的厕所\N{\rEng}As many toilets as I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.04,0:25:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人绝不会使用犹太人的厕所\N{\rEng}Germans never use Jewish toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们而言太干净了嘛\N{\rEng}They're too clean for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.22,0:25:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 拜托 帮帮我 先生\N{\rEng}Please, mister, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.67,0:25:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别想跑 你个小杂种\N{\rEng}Hold it! You little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.43,0:26:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 站住\N{\rEng}Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\rEng}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.33,0:26:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快 快 快来\N{\rEng}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.57,0:26:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 男孩\N{\rEng}Come on, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.34,0:26:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 站起来 站起来\N{\rEng}Stand up! Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.78,0:26:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 站起来\N{\rEng}Stand up! Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.38,0:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 就今晚这一次 别谈论任何不好的事情\N{\rEng}Please, tonight for once, I don't want anything bad talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.98,0:26:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享用这一餐\N{\rEng}Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.41,0:26:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那么我来说件有趣的事\N{\rEng}fine,Then I'll tell you something funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道罗席嘉先生吗\N{\rEng}You know who I mean by Dr. Raszeja?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.45,0:27:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-那位军医? -对 军医\N{\rEng}- The surgeon? - The surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别问我为什么 但因为某个原因\N{\rEng}for some reason and not ask me why
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.36,0:27:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人允许他到犹太人区做手术\N{\rEng}The Germans allowed him into the ghetto to perform an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.16,0:27:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对犹太人动刀?\N{\rEng}On a Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.36,0:27:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让波兰人为犹太人开刀?\N{\rEng}They let a Pole to come in to operate on a Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.43,0:27:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿到了通行证 我就知道这些 \N{\rEng}He got a pass, that's all I know. Anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他让病人昏睡过去然后开始动手术\N{\rEng}he puts the patient to sleep and starts the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.60,0:27:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他才刚划下第一刀 SS部队就闯进来\N{\rEng}He'd just made the first incision when the SS burst in...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.67,0:27:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,射杀了躺在病床上的病人 然后射杀罗席嘉医生\N{\rEng}shoot the patient lie on the table then shoot on Dr. Raszeja
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,接着是所有在场的人\N{\rEng}and everybody else who was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.08,0:27:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是很好笑\N{\rEng}Isn't that a laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.55,0:27:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那病人浑然不觉 因为他被麻醉了\N{\rEng}The patient didn't feel a thing, he was anesthetized.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.05,0:27:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过别讲扫兴的事 亨瑞\N{\rEng}I said nothing bad.Henryk
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.55,0:27:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了 都失去幽默感了吗\N{\rEng}What's the matter with you all? You lost your sense of humor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.36,0:27:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好笑\N{\rEng}It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.16,0:27:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什么东西好笑\N{\rEng}You know what's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.73,0:27:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你那条怪里怪气的领带才好笑\N{\rEng}You're funny, with that ridiculous tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.97,0:27:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛讲我的领带 我的领带招谁惹谁了\N{\rEng}You talk about my tie for what? What's my tie have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.37,0:27:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我上班需要这条领带\N{\rEng}I need this tie for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.90,0:27:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作\N{\rEng}Your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.60,0:27:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我在工作\N{\rEng}That's right, I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.47,0:27:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 弹钢琴给犹太区的那些寄生虫听\N{\rEng}Yes,your work. Playing the piano for the parasites in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.31,0:28:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-寄生虫 -孩子 孩子\N{\rEng}- Parasites... - Boys. Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.14,0:28:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对人们所受的苦无动于衷\N{\rEng}They don't give a damn about people some...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.76,0:28:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你因为他们的冷漠谴责我\N{\rEng}And you blame me for their apathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.11,0:28:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我每天看着这一切\N{\rEng}I do,because I see it everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至于对发生在周遭的事情无动于衷\N{\rEng}They don't even notice what's going around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.12,0:28:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要谴责美国人\N{\rEng}I blame the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.09,0:28:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 因为我的领带吗\N{\rEng}For what? For my tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.65,0:28:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,美国的犹太人 他们在那里人数不少\N{\rEng}The American Jews, and there are lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.42,0:28:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对我们做了什么 他们认为自己在做什么\N{\rEng}What do they done? What do they think they're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.53,0:28:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人因饥饿而亡\N{\rEng}People here are dying.Haven't got a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.96,0:28:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那里的犹太银行家应该督促美国对德国宣战\N{\rEng}The Jewish bankers should persuade America to declare war on Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.69,0:28:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,关灯 关灯\N{\rEng}The lights! The lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.73,0:29:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.25,0:29:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,开门 我们要进来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.50,0:29:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.51,0:29:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.38,0:29:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,把他丢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.03,0:30:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.93,0:30:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 我的天\N{\rEng}oh,please
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.07,0:30:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 我的天\N{\rEng}oh,my God
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.06,0:30:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,给我跑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.38,0:31:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我是席皮尔曼先生的姐姐\N{\rEng}Excuse men,I'm Mr. Szpilman's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.86,0:31:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好 进去吧 不是你\N{\rEng}Yeah,go in. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.57,0:31:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-发生什么事 -太可怕了\N{\rEng}- What's up? What's up? - It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.42,0:31:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在街上对人群扫射,他们抓走了亨瑞\N{\rEng}They're hunting people in the streets.They've taken Henryk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.18,0:32:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你先回家 好吗\N{\rEng}Go home, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.72,0:32:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你先回家 我来处理\N{\rEng}Go home,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.80,0:32:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请问一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.03,0:32:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看见我丈夫伊沙克·沙曼吗\N{\rEng}Have you seen my husband? Izaak Szerman?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.80,0:32:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕没有\N{\rEng}Afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.84,0:32:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他高大英俊 蓄着灰色胡子\N{\rEng}Tall, handsome, little gray beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.77,0:32:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有看见他 请写信通知我\N{\rEng}If you see him, write to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.37,0:32:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记 伊沙克·沙曼\N{\rEng}Don't forget. Izaak Szerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.45,0:32:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿发生了什么事\N{\rEng}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.26,0:32:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们带走了我孙子\N{\rEng}They've got my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.29,0:32:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们逮捕了他\N{\rEng}They pick them up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把他带走了\N{\rEng}and take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.46,0:32:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人对他们做了什么\N{\rEng}What do they do to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.79,0:32:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法再继续信仰上帝\N{\rEng}I've stopped believing in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 不好意思\N{\rEng}Excuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.97,0:32:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎克\N{\rEng}Itzak?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.34,0:32:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎克 伊扎克 是我 瓦列·席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Itzak? Itzak, it's Wladek Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.95,0:33:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亨瑞在里面\N{\rEng}Henryk is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.38,0:33:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有看见他\N{\rEng}I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 他们逮捕了他\N{\rEng}Believe me.They picked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.05,0:33:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.02,0:33:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮忙吗\N{\rEng}Can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.99,0:33:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你需要我了\N{\rEng}Now you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 现在你需要我了\N{\rEng}Yes,Now you need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.43,0:33:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮助我们吗\N{\rEng}Can you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.26,0:33:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱就帮\N{\rEng}It costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.40,0:33:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没钱\N{\rEng}I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.83,0:33:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没有我能效劳之处了\N{\rEng}Then there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.37,0:33:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当机会来的时候 你该加入我们的\N{\rEng}You should have joined us when you had chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.04,0:33:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎克 他们告诉我你有影响力\N{\rEng}Itzak,They told me you had influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.41,0:33:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的\N{\rEng}Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.54,0:33:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,人们\N{\rEng}People
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.98,0:33:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的人们 他们说你是重要人士\N{\rEng}People I know,They said you're an important man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.38,0:33:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎克\N{\rEng}Itzak...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.07,0:33:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.24,0:34:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好吗 -强盗 砰 砰 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.44,0:34:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-去死吧 把手举起来 -他是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.96,0:34:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-来一根不 -香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.08,0:34:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感恩不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.30,0:34:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他看上去可真无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.80,0:34:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.89,0:34:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.85,0:34:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手来 举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.94,0:34:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来人啊 帮帮我\N{\rEng}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.38,0:34:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,强盗 强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.28,0:34:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来人啊 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.53,0:35:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为何逮捕你\N{\rEng}Why they picked you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.87,0:35:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找了伊扎克·海勒?\N{\rEng}So you go to Itzak Heller?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.10,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有要你去找他吗\N{\rEng}Did I ask you to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.31,0:35:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你被放出来了 不是吗\N{\rEng}You're out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.87,0:35:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你求他了吗\N{\rEng}Did you beg
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.38,0:35:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你对那个人渣卑躬屈膝吗 -不 我请他帮助你\N{\rEng}- Did you bow to that piece of shit? - I asked him to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.41,0:35:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你付给他什么报酬\N{\rEng}What did you pay him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.55,0:35:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么可以给他 拿什么\N{\rEng}With what could I pay him? what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.32,0:35:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我赚的每分钱都花在食物上了\N{\rEng}Every zloty I earn were spend on food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.32,0:35:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以自己解决\N{\rEng}I can look after myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.32,0:35:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把你带走了\N{\rEng}They were taking you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.59,0:36:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那与你一点关系都没有\N{\rEng}It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.69,0:36:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抓的人是我 不是你\N{\rEng}It's me they wanted, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.69,0:36:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么一定要干涉别人的事情\N{\rEng}Why do you have to interfere with other people's business?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.23,0:36:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了 你的麻烦就是你疯了\N{\rEng}You're mad. That's your trouble.You are mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.37,0:36:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是我的事\N{\rEng}That's also my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.64,0:36:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}hey,what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.21,0:36:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你病了吗\N{\rEng}What's the matter? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.08,0:36:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了\N{\rEng}Hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.59,0:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就业许可证?\N{\rEng}Employment certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.76,0:36:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 没有就业许可证会怎样\N{\rEng}What's that mean, no employment certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.16,0:36:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要有就业许可证\N{\rEng}You have to have an employment certificate...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,才能在犹太区的德属公司工作 否则...\N{\rEng}to work for the Germans firms in the ghetto, otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.97,0:36:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,否则怎样\N{\rEng}Otherwise what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.40,0:36:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你会被驱逐\N{\rEng}You'll be deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么谣传是真的了\N{\rEng}So the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.87,0:36:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要重新处置我们\N{\rEng}They're going to resettle us...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.34,0:36:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们送到东边的集中营\N{\rEng}and send us to labor camps, in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.35,0:36:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们要关闭这个小犹太区\N{\rEng}They're closing the small ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.78,0:36:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.70,0:37:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列 瓦列\N{\rEng}Wladek? Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.74,0:37:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会到伦敦\N{\rEng}I thought you were on tour playing in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.09,0:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎 纽约 芝加哥巡回演出\N{\rEng} Paris, New York, Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个礼拜\N{\rEng}Not this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.57,0:37:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很糟\N{\rEng}You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.64,0:37:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你有听到谣传吗\N{\rEng}Have you heard the rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.18,0:37:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要把我们重新安置在东部\N{\rEng}They're going to resettle us in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.01,0:37:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谣传 你太把它们当一回事了\N{\rEng}Rumors! You take it all too much to heart.Wladek
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.75,0:37:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么麻烦吗\N{\rEng}What's the trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.35,0:37:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直试着帮我父亲申请一张工作许可证\N{\rEng}I've been trying to get the certificate of employment for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.82,0:37:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经设法帮我自己和我其他家人找到了\N{\rEng}I managed to get one for me and the rest of my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.96,0:37:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还需要另外一张给我父亲\N{\rEng}but I need another one for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.69,0:37:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经跑遍所有公司和商店\N{\rEng}I've been to all the firms and shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不来找我呢\N{\rEng}Why didn't you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.00,0:37:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在处理许可证的业务\N{\rEng}I didn't know you were in the certificate business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我 是梅耶克\N{\rEng}I'm not, but Majorek is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.84,0:37:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮忙吗 但我没钱\N{\rEng}Can you help? I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-拜托 别贬低我们 -你可以为他做点什么吗\N{\rEng}- Please, don't insult us. -Can you do something for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.74,0:38:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,明天四点到修兹工作室\N{\rEng}Be at the Schultz workshop tomorrow, four o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.61,0:38:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你今天运气有多好\N{\rEng}See what a wonderful piece of luck you've had today?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.51,0:38:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,命中注定啊\N{\rEng}That's the historical imperative in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.18,0:38:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我常说的 要看好的那一面\N{\rEng}That's why I always say "Look on the bright side!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.32,0:38:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好的那一面 是 我知道\N{\rEng}The bright side,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的背怎样了\N{\rEng}How's your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.54,0:38:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了\N{\rEng}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.80,0:38:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了吗\N{\rEng}Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.01,0:38:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已经好多了\N{\rEng}Better than ask
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.05,0:38:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.72,0:38:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气 虽然我什么忙也帮不上\N{\rEng}My pleasure. Won't help you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 修兹先生\N{\rEng}Thank you, Mr. Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.31,0:39:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（1942年3月15日）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.97,0:40:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们在犹太区找到工作了\N{\rEng}At least we got work in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.07,0:40:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们都还在一起\N{\rEng}At least we are still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全部出去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.56,0:40:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到院子去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.29,0:40:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别站着不动
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.29,0:40:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是雇员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.96,0:40:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有工作证
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.43,0:40:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.31,0:40:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.60,0:40:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去那里 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.81,0:40:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.45,0:40:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.78,0:40:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.42,0:40:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.79,0:41:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.70,0:41:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的人穿好衣服回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.37,0:41:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,带着你们的东西 最多15公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您要把我们送去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.50,0:41:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我已经尽力了\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为工作证可以拯救我们\N{\rEng}I thought the certificates'd save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.34,0:41:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 瓦列\N{\rEng}Stop it, Wladek.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.48,0:41:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我们一心期望亨瑞和哈琳娜安然无恙\N{\rEng}Let's just hope that Henryk and Halina will be better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.08,0:42:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（1942年8月16日）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.64,0:42:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要到哪里去\N{\rEng}Where will we be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.08,0:42:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去工作\N{\rEng}Going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.38,0:42:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会比待在那个臭气熏天的犹太区好多了 向前走\N{\rEng}You'll be much better off than in the stinking ghetto. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.22,0:42:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.55,0:42:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.26,0:42:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.46,0:42:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.86,0:42:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.74,0:42:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.74,0:42:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做 我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it? Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.78,0:43:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.05,0:43:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.58,0:43:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有水吗\N{\rEng}Don't you have a bottle of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.61,0:43:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他快死了 我的孩子快要渴死了\N{\rEng}He's dying.My child is dying of thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.55,0:43:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-我求求你 求求你 -我很抱歉 \N{\rEng}- I beg you.I beg you. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.52,0:43:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你有水吗 求求你\N{\rEng}Don't you have a bottle of water? I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.35,0:43:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到我说的话吗\N{\rEng}Did you hear what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.65,0:43:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 这是一个耻辱\N{\rEng}I'm telling you, it's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.32,0:43:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在听\N{\rEng}I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.02,0:43:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们任凭他们把我们引向死亡 就像羔羊走向屠场\N{\rEng}Letting them take us to our death like sheep to the slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.53,0:43:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么大声\N{\rEng}Not so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.53,0:43:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们何不反击\N{\rEng}Why don't we attack them?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.89,0:43:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有五十万人在这里 我们可以突破犹太区重围\N{\rEng}There's half a million of us here. We can break out of the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.33,0:43:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们可以光荣地死去\N{\rEng}At least we can die honorably,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.66,0:43:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是当历史上的一个污点\N{\rEng}not as a stain on the face of History.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.23,0:43:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为何你这么确定\N{\rEng}Why are you so sure
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.34,0:43:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会送我们下黄泉\N{\rEng}they're sending us to our death?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.37,0:44:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\rEng}I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.40,0:44:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么我不能确定吗\N{\rEng}You know why I'm not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.47,0:44:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们又没告诉我\N{\rEng}Because they didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.64,0:44:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要把我们赶尽杀绝\N{\rEng}They're going to wipe us all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.38,0:44:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我怎么做 你要我抗争吗\N{\rEng}Tell me what do you want me to do? Do you want me to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.68,0:44:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抗争的话需要组织 计划 枪支...\N{\rEng}To fight, we need organization, plans, guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.95,0:44:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他说得没错 你认为我能做什么\N{\rEng}He's right. Do you think I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.35,0:44:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的小提琴弓抗争吗\N{\rEng}to fight with my violin bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.05,0:44:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人不会浪费像这样庞大的劳力\N{\rEng}The Germans would never squander a huge labor force like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.55,0:44:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显地他们正要把我们送到集中营\N{\rEng}They're sending us to a labor camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 当然 看看那个瘸子\N{\rEng}oh,Sure. Look at that cripple there,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.66,0:44:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些老人跟小孩 他们也要工作吗\N{\rEng}the old people, the children. They're going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.86,0:44:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你 你要带着背上的铁架一起去吗\N{\rEng}Look at you. You're going to carry logs on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.74,0:45:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,亨瑞\N{\rEng}Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.24,0:45:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈莲娜 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Halina, Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哈莲娜 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Halina, Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.45,0:45:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听说你们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.89,0:45:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要跟你们在一起\N{\rEng}I wanted to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.80,0:45:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要跟你们在一起\N{\rEng}I wanted to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.97,0:45:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋\N{\rEng}Stupid. Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.14,0:45:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎能这样做 我怎能这样做\N{\rEng}Why did I do it? Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.88,0:45:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她让我神经紧张\N{\rEng}She's getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.02,0:45:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷 她到底做了什么\N{\rEng}What did she do, for God's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.75,0:45:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她闷死了她的婴儿\N{\rEng}She smothered her baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.12,0:46:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们准备了一个隐匿处 他们都躲在那里\N{\rEng}They prepared a hiding place and of course they went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.93,0:46:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当警察来的时候 婴儿哭了起来\N{\rEng}The baby cried just as the police came.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.80,0:46:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她用手捂住啼哭的婴儿\N{\rEng}She smothered the cries with her hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.63,0:46:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,婴儿就这么死了\N{\rEng}the baby died.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.34,0:46:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有个警察听见了声响\N{\rEng}A policeman heard the death rattle
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.01,0:46:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,发现他们的藏身之处\N{\rEng}and found where they were hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.35,0:46:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rEng}mama
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.20,0:46:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在读什么\N{\rEng}What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.00,0:46:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,若你戳刺我们 我们不会流血吗\N{\rEng}"If you prick us, de we not bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.31,0:46:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,若你挠我们痒 我们不会发笑吗\N{\rEng}If you tickle us, do we not laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.98,0:46:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,若你对我们下毒 我们不会死去吗\N{\rEng}If you poison us, do we not die?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.08,0:46:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,若你加害于我们 我们不应该复仇吗\N{\rEng}And, if you wrong us,shall we not revenge?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.32,0:47:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,写得很好\N{\rEng}Very appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.72,0:47:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 这就是我带着它的原因\N{\rEng}Yes. That's why I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.64,0:47:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个傻瓜 他觉得在这儿赚钱还有用吗\N{\rEng}Idiot. What does he think he's gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.35,0:47:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 男孩\N{\rEng}Boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.35,0:47:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里\N{\rEng}come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.89,0:47:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.89,0:47:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一块奶糖要多少钱\N{\rEng}How much for a caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.06,0:47:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.49,0:47:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 一块奶糖要要这么多\N{\rEng}What? For one caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.83,0:47:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要怎么花这些钱\N{\rEng}What do you think you're gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.56,0:47:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.56,0:47:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谁有20波币吗\N{\rEng}We've got 20 between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.97,0:47:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我有10元\N{\rEng}I've got 10, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.31,0:47:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,5、10、20\N{\rEng}5, 10, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.83,0:49:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈琳娜 -什么\N{\rEng}- Halina? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.97,0:49:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说这个挺怪的 但是...\N{\rEng}It's a funny time to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.41,0:49:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.04,0:49:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿我能多了解你一些\N{\rEng}I wish I knew you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.32,0:49:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.67,0:49:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Szpilman
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.67,0:49:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Szpilman
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.61,0:50:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 笨蛋 走
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.18,0:50:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa? Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.32,0:50:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}papa
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.05,0:50:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 哈琳娜\N{\rEng}Mama? Halina?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.92,0:50:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哈琳娜 妈妈\N{\rEng}Halina? Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.86,0:50:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为自己在干嘛 席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}What do you think you're doing,Szpilman?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.59,0:50:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你一命\N{\rEng}I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.63,0:50:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,起来 快走 走\N{\rEng}Just get up,go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.80,0:50:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别用跑的\N{\rEng}Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.77,0:50:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜 安娜 安娜\N{\rEng}Anna!Anna!Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.83,0:50:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好 把他们送去彻底改造
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.16,0:50:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.97,0:51:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个留下 把它给我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.14,0:51:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 她是孕妇\N{\rEng}What are you doing? She's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.28,0:51:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,向左转
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.29,0:51:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,齐步走
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.76,0:53:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列\N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.95,0:54:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里 瓦列\N{\rEng}Why are you here, Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.15,0:54:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 我 我\N{\rEng}It's like this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.52,0:54:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们...\N{\rEng}We...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.76,0:54:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所有人 他们所有人\N{\rEng}All of them, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.16,0:54:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所有人\N{\rEng}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.43,0:54:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们够幸运 早登极乐\N{\rEng}Perhaps they're lucky. The quicker, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.54,0:54:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还没有结束 我们将在这里待上些日子\N{\rEng}It's not finished yet. We'll stay here for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.67,0:54:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直到尘埃落定\N{\rEng}until things die down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.84,0:54:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经贿赂了一个警察 事情结束的时候他会过来\N{\rEng}I've bribed the policeman, he'll come when it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.56,0:54:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,立正 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.32,0:54:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.80,0:54:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 我已经有二年没有出去过了\N{\rEng}My God, I haven't been outside in, it must be two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.17,0:54:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别太激动\N{\rEng}Don't get overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.79,0:55:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,黄金\N{\rEng}gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.92,0:55:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这价钱很好\N{\rEng}Very good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.31,0:55:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有认识的人吗\N{\rEng}Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.61,0:55:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个美人是谁\N{\rEng}A beauty. Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.62,0:55:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个歌手 事实上我跟她很熟\N{\rEng}She's a singer. I knew her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.35,0:55:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她丈夫是演员\N{\rEng}Her husband is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是好人\N{\rEng}They're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.66,0:55:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟她说话\N{\rEng}I'd like to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.59,0:55:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记 帮助犹太人的会被德国人绞死\N{\rEng}Don't forget, Wladek.They hang them for helping Jews.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.21,0:56:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,向左转
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.79,0:56:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.47,0:56:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.68,0:56:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.58,0:56:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,出列
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.83,0:57:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.67,0:57:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.96,0:57:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.76,0:57:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.01,0:57:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.46,0:57:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.75,0:57:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.35,0:58:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里待多久了\N{\rEng}How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.92,0:58:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚开始的\N{\rEng}Since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.06,0:58:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴遇见你\N{\rEng}I was pleased to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.33,0:58:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在即将开始进行最后的安置\N{\rEng}They're going to start the final resettlement now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.50,0:58:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道那意味着什么\N{\rEng}We know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.97,0:58:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们送了一个人出去 席格蒙 他是个好人\N{\rEng}We sent someone out. Zygmund, a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.48,0:59:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他受命追踪从华沙发出的列车\N{\rEng}His orders were to follow the trains out of Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.25,0:59:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他抵达索克洛\N{\rEng}He got to Sokolow.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.55,0:59:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一位当地的铁道员告诉他 轨道在那里分路而行\N{\rEng}A man told him the tracks divided,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.46,0:59:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一条通往催布林卡\N{\rEng}one branch's leading to Treblinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.26,0:59:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他说每天运货列车载着满车的人从华沙驶来\N{\rEng}He said everyday freight trains carrying people from Warsaw...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.26,0:59:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开往催布林卡的方向 然后空车返回\N{\rEng}branch off to Treblinka and return empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.43,0:59:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在那条路线上 从没看过有食物运送\N{\rEng}No transports of food are ever seen on that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.17,0:59:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而居民...被禁止靠近催布林卡车站\N{\rEng}The civilians are forbidden to approach the Treblinka station.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.75,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想把我们赶尽杀绝\N{\rEng}They're exterminating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.92,0:59:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那用不着花太多时间\N{\rEng}It won't take them long.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.92,0:59:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,从50万人到现在 我们只剩下6万人\N{\rEng}We are 60 thousand left, out of half a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.33,0:59:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎都是年轻人\N{\rEng}Mostly young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.23,0:59:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而这一次我们要反抗\N{\rEng}And this time we're gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.04,0:59:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们状况良好 组织健全\N{\rEng}We're in good shape.Organized.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.07,1:00:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经准备好了\N{\rEng}We're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.14,1:00:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要援助 我...\N{\rEng}If you need help, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.10,1:00:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你 过来\N{\rEng}You! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.57,1:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 可恶 可恶\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.75,1:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我很抱歉\N{\rEng}sorry.I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.21,1:00:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我刚刚失了神\N{\rEng}I don't know what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.49,1:00:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 拜托 不要 拜托\N{\rEng}please, please
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.66,1:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rEng}please
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.68,1:01:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把他拖走
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.23,1:01:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你弹钢琴的功夫比砌砖好\N{\rEng}I hope you play the piano better than you carry bricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.00,1:01:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会撑太久的 如果他继续这样下去\N{\rEng}He won't last long if he goes on like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.74,1:01:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看我是否能让他好过一点\N{\rEng}I'll see if I can get him something better.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.10,1:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有麻烦\N{\rEng}Trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.87,1:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,集合 只有犹太人\N{\rEng}Round up! Only the Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.14,1:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,波兰人继续干活 犹太人集合\N{\rEng}The Polish keep working. Only the Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.98,1:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好消息要告诉你们\N{\rEng}I have good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.75,1:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都有谣言...\N{\rEng}There are rumors going around that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.86,1:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要 呃...\N{\rEng}we like to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.46,1:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,重新安置你们\N{\rEng}to resettle you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.06,1:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证 从今以后\N{\rEng}I promise you that now and in the future...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.14,1:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没有新计划\N{\rEng}nothing else is planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.87,1:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,基于这个原因\N{\rEng}For this reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.68,1:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在墙上贴公报\N{\rEng}we put information posters on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.48,1:02:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了表示我们的善意\N{\rEng}To show you our goodwill...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.02,1:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,应该推举你们当中某一个人...\N{\rEng}you should vote one of you to be allowed...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.45,1:03:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他获准每天进城...\N{\rEng}to go in town daily...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.53,1:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,带回三公斤的马铃薯...\N{\rEng}and bring 3 kilos of potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.07,1:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一条面包...\N{\rEng}and one loaf of bread
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.43,1:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,给你们每一个工人\N{\rEng}for each of your workers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.54,1:03:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们真的要重新安置你们\N{\rEng}So, why should we do something like this
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.37,1:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为何还要这样做呢\N{\rEng}if we'd resettle you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.38,1:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以用不吃的东西\N{\rEng}You can make good business
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.01,1:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好好做生意\N{\rEng}out of the things you don't eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.95,1:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是是你们犹太人最擅长的吗\N{\rEng}Isn't that something that you Jews are good in?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.05,1:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,赚钱\N{\rEng}Making money?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.93,1:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.38,1:03:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...是用绳子绑的\N{\rEng}That one, with the string.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.51,1:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,其它的用铁线绑\N{\rEng}The others, tied by wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.05,1:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rEng}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.79,1:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,梅耶克\N{\rEng}Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.53,1:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请你帮我一个忙\N{\rEng}I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.90,1:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要离开这里\N{\rEng}I want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.30,1:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要出去很容易\N{\rEng}It's easy to get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.84,1:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,困难的是你要如何在外面存活下来\N{\rEng}It's how you survive on the other side,that's hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.84,1:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 我明白\N{\rEng}I know.I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.84,1:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去年夏天\N{\rEng}Last summer,I worked for a day
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.71,1:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾在兹兰那 布拉马广场工作了一天\N{\rEng}in the Zelazna Brama Square.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.18,1:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见一个认识的人 她是个老朋友了\N{\rEng}I saw someone I knew, she's an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.68,1:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一位歌手 她丈夫是个演员\N{\rEng}A singer, her husband is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.79,1:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我写下他们的名字跟地址\N{\rEng}I've filled their names down and their address,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.29,1:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们还住在原处的话\N{\rEng}if they're still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.03,1:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雅尼娜·歌德瓦斯卡卡和安德兹·博克基\N{\rEng}Janina Godlewska and Andrzej Bogucki.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.03,1:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是好人\N{\rEng}They're good people.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.56,1:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能试着连络上他们吗\N{\rEng}Would you try to make contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.00,1:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天都进城 你能问问他们...\N{\rEng}You go to town everyday, would you just ask them...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.31,1:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,问他们是否能帮我逃离这里\N{\rEng}Ask them if they'd help me get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.77,1:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有药膏吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.65,1:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你上来做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.72,1:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.39,1:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们获准把食物带进犹太区
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.56,1:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,3公斤的马铃薯和面包
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.60,1:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.97,1:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,马铃薯和面包
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.14,1:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说谎 我嗅到你的谎言了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.77,1:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.11,1:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,马铃薯?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.88,1:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们犹太人都一样
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.82,1:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们犹太人...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.69,1:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...总是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.62,1:08:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.11,1:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再骗我 我就把你给毙了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.88,1:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我以名义起誓
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.50,1:09:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着去找你的朋友\N{\rEng}I tried your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.67,1:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有住在那里了\N{\rEng}They don't live there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.97,1:09:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那...你联络到了吗\N{\rEng}Did you make contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.14,1:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以准备离开了\N{\rEng}Be ready to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.51,1:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,何时\N{\rEng}When?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.41,1:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快\N{\rEng}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.28,1:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,立定\N{\rEng}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.11,1:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.10,1:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我教你们什么叫纪律 犹太猪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.44,1:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,知道为什么要扁你们吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.94,1:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 -知道为什么要扁你们吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.28,1:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.51,1:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为了欢庆新年
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.18,1:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 前进
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.58,1:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,前进 把歌唱起来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.69,1:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,唱点让人振奋的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.29,1:10:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大声地唱 整齐地唱
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.58,1:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚再次相聚 跟随白色雄鹰
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.75,1:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来反抗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.91,1:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不共戴天的敌人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.91,1:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这天站起来 向他们投炮火和硫磺
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.42,1:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会摆脱奴隶的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.46,1:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,惩罚并击败我们民族的践踏者
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.71,1:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要铲除他们 挽救我们的尊严
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.31,1:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.13,1:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我脏兮兮的\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.I'm dirty. I'm so filthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.89,1:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有太多时间 来吧\N{\rEng}We haven't much time.Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.30,1:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得快一点\N{\rEng}We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.44,1:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 看看合不合身\N{\rEng}Here. See if this fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.31,1:13:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得一直换地方\N{\rEng}We have to keep moving
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.61,1:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人现在不分青红皂白地搜捕\N{\rEng}Germans are hunting down indiscriminately now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.21,1:13:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人 非犹太人 任何人 每一个人\N{\rEng}Jews, non-Jews, anybody, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.65,1:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列 你最好刮一下胡子\N{\rEng}Wladek,You better shave.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.08,1:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,用我架子上的刮胡刀\N{\rEng}Use my razor on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.53,1:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,马里克·吉勃克辛斯基会照顾你的\N{\rEng}You'll be looked after by Gebczynski.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.47,1:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他住在城的另一边\N{\rEng}He's on the other side of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.77,1:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚你就待在那里 我们会再帮你找新的住处\N{\rEng}You stay there tonight, then we'll find you somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.28,1:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带食物给你\N{\rEng}I'll bring you food.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.65,1:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们走了\N{\rEng}Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.89,1:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去看你睡觉的地方\N{\rEng}I'll show you where you're going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.29,1:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须在这边待到明天下午\N{\rEng}You have to stay here until tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.42,1:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在犹太区围墙附近为你准备了公寓\N{\rEng}We have a flat for you near the ghetto wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.86,1:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那里很安全\N{\rEng}But it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.60,1:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不太舒适\N{\rEng}It's not going to be very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.61,1:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很好了\N{\rEng}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.32,1:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.30,1:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我来拿 给我\N{\rEng}Here. Here. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.67,1:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量向前走 靠近德国区\N{\rEng}Go as near to the front as possible,to the German section.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.83,1:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（请勿穿过）
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.86,1:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要拉下窗帘\N{\rEng}I'm going to draw the curtains now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.87,1:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,白天要打开窗帘\N{\rEng}But you leave them open during the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.87,1:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要记住\N{\rEng}Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.51,1:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在墙的这一边一定会好过些吧\N{\rEng}Must feel better on this side of the wall,eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.95,1:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.95,1:17:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时候我仍不确定自己是在墙的哪一边\N{\rEng}But sometimes I'm still not sure which side of the wall I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.29,1:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有些面包... 马铃薯 洋葱\N{\rEng}Some bread,potatoes,onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.09,1:17:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来的\N{\rEng}I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.39,1:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有雅尼娜·歌德瓦斯卡 每周会来看你二次\N{\rEng}Janina will visit you twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.76,1:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,给你带更多食物 看看你好不好\N{\rEng}bring more food,see how you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.63,1:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.77,1:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个非常重要\N{\rEng}This is very important.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.07,1:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果万一发生紧急状况... 我是说非常紧急...\N{\rEng}In case of emergency...I mean emergency,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.48,1:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到这个地址去\N{\rEng}go to this address.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.45,1:18:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 你说忘记是什么意思\N{\rEng}Fuck you dog,what do you mean you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.89,1:18:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我是什么意思\N{\rEng}What do you think I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.72,1:18:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思就是我忘记了\N{\rEng}I forgot,that's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.16,1:18:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你待我如粪土\N{\rEng}You know what,you treat me like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.43,1:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我待你如粪土 因为你就是粪土\N{\rEng}Treat you like dirt? Because you are a dirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.63,1:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,猪头 猪头 \N{\rEng}Pig! Pig!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.93,1:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-婊子 你是只肮脏的猪猡\N{\rEng}- Bitch!You are a dirty pig!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.37,1:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此 猪头\N{\rEng}Takes one to know one. Pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.44,1:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你弹琴时像个天使\N{\rEng}Um,you play like an angel,catskin.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.71,1:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我弹琴像个天使 你为什么不听\N{\rEng}If i look like an angel,why don't you listen?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.32,1:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我有听啊 小喵咪\N{\rEng}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.75,1:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子 你明明睡着了 小猪头\N{\rEng}Liar.You fell asleep. Pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.26,1:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（1943年4月19日）
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.47,1:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,散开 我们遭到袭击了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.02,1:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,藏起来
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.11,1:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.20,1:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,隐蔽 开火
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.25,1:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 跑呀
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.80,1:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,射击 射击\N{\rEng}fire!fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.70,1:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,偷袭成功
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.31,1:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（1943年5月16日）
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.11,1:21:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那栋楼...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.90,1:21:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.85,1:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.08,1:22:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.15,1:22:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-我本想早点来的 但... -不不不 谢谢你\N{\rEng}- I wanted to come earlier,but... - No,thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.46,1:22:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没人想到会他们会坚持这么久\N{\rEng}No one thought they'd hold out so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.53,1:22:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该出来的\N{\rEng}I never should've come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.90,1:22:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该留在那里 与他们一起战斗\N{\rEng}I should have stayed and fought with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.13,1:22:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列 别那么说\N{\rEng}Wladyslaw,stop that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.07,1:22:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都结束了\N{\rEng}It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.84,1:22:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你该为他们感到骄傲\N{\rEng}Just be proud of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.94,1:22:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 他们发起了抗争\N{\rEng}My God,did they put up a fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.31,1:22:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.54,1:22:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人也是\N{\rEng}So did the Germans.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.95,1:22:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常震惊\N{\rEng}They were in shock!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.55,1:22:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有预料到 没有人预料得到\N{\rEng}They didn't expect it. Nobody expected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.68,1:23:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人反抗了\N{\rEng}Jews fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.49,1:23:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会想到呢\N{\rEng}Who would thought?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.39,1:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么用呢\N{\rEng}What good did it do?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.19,1:23:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么用\N{\rEng}What good?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.49,1:23:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列 你真让我吃惊\N{\rEng}Wladek,I'm surprised with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.30,1:23:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们死得有尊严 这就是意义\N{\rEng}They died with dignity.That what good they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.97,1:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你知道吗\N{\rEng}And you know something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.00,1:23:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在波兰人也要觉醒了\N{\rEng}Now the Poles will rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.37,1:23:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了\N{\rEng}We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.31,1:23:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也要抗争 你知道吗\N{\rEng}We'll fight too. You see.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.32,1:23:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的东西收拾好 你必须离开\N{\rEng}Get your things together.You have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.93,1:23:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 发生什么事了\N{\rEng}What? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.93,1:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要逃亡了\N{\rEng}I'm on the run.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.27,1:23:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\rEng}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.27,1:23:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密警察发现我们的武器了\N{\rEng}The Gestapo found our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.27,1:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经逮捕了雅尼娜和安德兹\N{\rEng}They've arrested Janina and Andrzej.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.47,1:23:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也将要查出这个地方 \N{\rEng}They're bound to find out about this place too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.26,1:23:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须马上离开\N{\rEng} You must get away at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.70,1:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我到哪里去\N{\rEng}Where do you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.18,1:24:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\rEng}Look at me,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.54,1:24:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要走 \N{\rEng}I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.67,1:24:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能留在这里 冒险一试吗\N{\rEng}Can I take my chances here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.00,1:24:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己决定 \N{\rEng}That's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.31,1:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当他们突击公寓的时候 从窗户跳出去\N{\rEng}But when they storm the flat,throw yourself out the window...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.12,1:24:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们活捉你 \N{\rEng}don't let them get you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.81,1:24:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上有毒药  他们也不可能活捉我\N{\rEng}I have poison on me. They won't get me alive either.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.53,1:27:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rEng}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.92,1:27:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,马上开门 不然我们要叫警察来了\N{\rEng}Open the door or we'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.77,1:28:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这栋公寓的人吗\N{\rEng}Are you from this flat?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.05,1:28:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有登记 \N{\rEng}You're not registered.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.79,1:28:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我朋友的房子\N{\rEng}It belongs to a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.37,1:28:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来拜访他  但他不在家\N{\rEng}I just came to visit,but not,I just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.67,1:28:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你有身份证吗\N{\rEng}Have you got your identity card?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.23,1:28:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看你的身份证\N{\rEng}Let me see your identity card.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.40,1:28:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Yes,of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.24,1:28:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看你的身份证\N{\rEng}I want to see your identity card!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.81,1:28:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.69,1:28:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他是犹太人 犹太人 拦住这个犹太人\N{\rEng}He's a Jew! A Jew! Stop the Jew!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.03,1:28:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他出去 拦住他\N{\rEng}Don't let him out!Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.91,1:29:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.48,1:29:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉勃克辛斯基先生要我来的\N{\rEng}Mr. Gebczynski sent me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.38,1:30:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列迪斯洛·席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Wladyslaw Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.16,1:30:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝塔 \N{\rEng}Dorota.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.37,1:30:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 \N{\rEng}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.32,1:30:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.I...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.16,1:30:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有人给我这个地址\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.I was given this address.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.97,1:30:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我来找一位德兹奇威兹先生\N{\rEng}and I'm looking for a Mr. Dzikiewicz.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.25,1:30:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克·德兹奇威兹是我的丈夫\N{\rEng}Michael Dzikiewicz,he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.55,1:30:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 \N{\rEng}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.54,1:30:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,坐\N{\rEng}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.82,1:30:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要帮助 \N{\rEng}I need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.73,1:30:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他会在宵禁之前回来\N{\rEng}He'll be back before curfew.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.69,1:30:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在躲藏\N{\rEng}I've been in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.29,1:30:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个藏身之处\N{\rEng}I need somewhere to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.76,1:30:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他就快回来了\N{\rEng}Be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.60,1:30:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚多久了\N{\rEng}How long have you been married?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.63,1:31:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,才满一年\N{\rEng}Just over a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.77,1:31:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,裘瑞克怎么样了\N{\rEng}And how is Jurek?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.44,1:31:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\N{\rEng}Dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.88,1:31:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的宝宝什么时候出世\N{\rEng}When is your baby due?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.02,1:31:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节\N{\rEng}Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.32,1:31:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是养育小孩的好时机 但当时...\N{\rEng}This is not a good time to have children,but then...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.52,1:31:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我先生 这是瓦列迪斯洛·席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}This is my husband. Wladyslaw Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.19,1:31:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,马里克·吉勃克辛斯基要他来的\N{\rEng}Marek Gebczynski sent him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.73,1:31:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我记得\N{\rEng}Yes,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.80,1:31:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吉勃克辛斯基说过只有在紧急时才来找你\N{\rEng}Mr. Gebczynski said to contact you only in case of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.57,1:31:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不用担心了\N{\rEng}Don't worry now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.48,1:31:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我们不能把你送走 你就睡在沙发\N{\rEng}We can't move you tonight.You'll sleep on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.52,1:32:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.10,1:32:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我可以吃片面包吗\N{\rEng}I'm sorry,could I have a piece of bread?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.30,1:32:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我们一起吃\N{\rEng}Yes,of course.We will eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.80,1:32:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,坐 请坐\N{\rEng}Sit. Please,sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.64,1:32:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.70,1:34:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在正置身德国区\N{\rEng}You're on a very German area.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.97,1:34:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对面的建筑物是一家医院 \N{\rEng}Building on the opposite is a hospital
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.97,1:34:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,收容从俄国前线回来的伤兵\N{\rEng}taking wounded from the Russian front.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.21,1:34:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它隔壁就是纳粹党卫军\N{\rEng}And next door is the Schutzpolizei.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.98,1:34:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最安全的地方\N{\rEng}Safest place to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.39,1:34:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在狮子巢穴的正中心\N{\rEng}Right at the heart of the lion's den.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.53,1:34:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你锁在里面\N{\rEng}I'll be locking you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.93,1:34:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人知道你在这里 所以尽可能保持安静\N{\rEng}No one knows you're here,so keep as quiet as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.30,1:37:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧\N{\rEng}All well?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.07,1:37:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.57,1:37:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是安提克·札勒斯\N{\rEng}This is Antek Szalas.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.61,1:37:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他将会照顾你\N{\rEng}He'll be looking after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.61,1:37:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 -你好\N{\rEng}- How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.65,1:37:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.58,1:37:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给了他一把备用钥匙\N{\rEng}I've given him a second key.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.02,1:37:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他会带食物给你 看你是否安然无恙\N{\rEng}He'll bring food,see that you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.12,1:37:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他是地下组织成员 人很好\N{\rEng}He's with the underground,he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.79,1:37:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得我了 席皮尔曼先生\N{\rEng}You don't remember me?Mr Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.73,1:37:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不记得了\N{\rEng}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.40,1:37:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,华沙广播电台 我是一个技术人员\N{\rEng}Warsaw Radio. I was a technician.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.23,1:37:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎每天都看见你\N{\rEng}I saw you almost everyday.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.97,1:37:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不记得了 我...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry,I don't remember.I...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.71,1:37:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有关系\N{\rEng}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.68,1:37:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用担心任何事情 我会常来看你的\N{\rEng}You've nothing to worry about. I'll visit often.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.35,1:37:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很高兴听到同盟国正在轰炸德国...\N{\rEng}You'll be pleased to hear that the Allies are bombing Germany...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.92,1:38:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,夜复一夜 夜复一夜\N{\rEng}night after night,after night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.45,1:38:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,科隆 汉堡 柏林\N{\rEng}Cologne,Hamburg,Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.82,1:38:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而俄国人将会真正把他们带入地狱\N{\rEng}And the Russians are really giving them hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.13,1:38:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是终结的开始\N{\rEng}It's the beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.49,1:38:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿如此\N{\rEng}Oh,Let's hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.89,1:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.27,1:38:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.40,1:38:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个 小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.17,1:38:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着吗\N{\rEng}Still alive then?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.35,1:39:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有香肠 面包\N{\rEng}Here. Sausage,bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.65,1:39:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那瓶伏特加还没喝完吗\N{\rEng}You still got that vodka?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.97,1:39:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这还得持续多久呢\N{\rEng}How long is this meant to last?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.44,1:39:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不久了\N{\rEng}Not long now.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.87,1:39:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我想...我得了黄疸\N{\rEng}I thin…think I've got jaundice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.21,1:39:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心那个\N{\rEng}You don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.08,1:39:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是让你看起来比较好笑\N{\rEng}Just makes you look funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.25,1:39:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我爷爷当年出黄疸时被他女朋友甩了\N{\rEng}My grandfather was jilted by his girlfriend when he got jaundice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.45,1:39:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喝光它\N{\rEng}Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.22,1:39:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为...为什么你不早一点来\N{\rEng}Why...why didn't you come sooner?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.89,1:39:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已经超过二个礼拜了\N{\rEng}It's been over two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.36,1:39:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到点麻烦\N{\rEng}Problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.39,1:39:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,钱\N{\rEng}Money.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.93,1:39:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须筹钱买食物\N{\rEng}I've got to raise money to buy the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.83,1:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要可以卖的东西\N{\rEng}I need things to sell,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.47,1:39:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这不容易\N{\rEng}it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.34,1:40:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 把它卖了\N{\rEng}Here. Sell this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.54,1:40:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,食物比时间重要\N{\rEng}Food is more important than time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.22,1:40:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我要告诉你\N{\rEng}Oh,yes. I meant to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.59,1:40:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,盟军已经在法国登陆了\N{\rEng}The Allies have landed in France.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.32,1:40:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国军队就快要到这里了\N{\rEng}Russians will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.06,1:40:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把狗娘养的德国人赶走...\N{\rEng}They'll beat the shit out of the Germans...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.86,1:40:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都可能到\N{\rEng}any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.97,1:41:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\rEng}No No No
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.87,1:41:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列\N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.45,1:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦列\N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.55,1:41:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道 我就知道这会发生\N{\rEng}I knew it.I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.49,1:41:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要去找医生 -你不能去 这样太危险了\N{\rEng}- I'll get a doctor - You can't. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.79,1:41:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找路札克医生 我们可以信任他\N{\rEng}Dr. Luczak. We can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.63,1:41:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝塔 别傻了 他是儿科医生\N{\rEng}Ridiculous.Don't be stupid.He's a pediatrician.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.86,1:41:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是医生\N{\rEng}He's still a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.03,1:41:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你留下 我去找\N{\rEng}No.You stay. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.87,1:42:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来道别的\N{\rEng}We came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.97,1:42:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要到奥特沃茨克跟我妈妈在一起\N{\rEng}We're going to stay with my mother in Otwocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.11,1:42:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,宝宝已经在那里了 那里更安全\N{\rEng}The baby is already there.It's safer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.61,1:42:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,据说暴动随时都有可能开始\N{\rEng}There's talk that the uprising will begin any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.02,1:42:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,札勒斯可能被射杀了\N{\rEng}That man Szalas should be shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.65,1:42:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他以你的名义在华沙到处筹款\N{\rEng}He's been collecting money on your behalf all over Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.66,1:42:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,显然人们慷慨解囊\N{\rEng}Apparently people gave generously,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.63,1:42:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他筹到了一笔可观的数目\N{\rEng}so he collected a tidy sum.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.83,1:42:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.94,1:42:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,肝脏肿得像颗橄榄球\N{\rEng}The liver the size of a football.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.91,1:42:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,胆囊有严重的发炎\N{\rEng}Inflammation of the gall bladder...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.88,1:42:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但他会活着\N{\rEng}but he'll live.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.45,1:43:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尝试给他用些左旋糖\N{\rEng}I'll try to get him some laevulose,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.79,1:43:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但这并不容易\N{\rEng}but it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.99,1:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以再来看他吗\N{\rEng}Can you visit him again?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.39,1:43:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不确定\N{\rEng}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.59,1:43:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\rEng}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.76,1:43:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢你 -别说话 休息\N{\rEng}- thank you. - Don't speak,rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.57,1:43:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感激你过来\N{\rEng}Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.81,1:43:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你带来一些食物\N{\rEng}We brought you some food.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.24,1:43:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要为你准备些东西\N{\rEng}I'll prepare something now for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.11,1:43:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就得走了\N{\rEng}then we must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.58,1:43:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（1944年8月1日）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.04,1:44:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有个受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.09,1:44:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,出来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.76,1:44:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当心点 当心点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.30,1:44:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-我去找人帮忙 -快点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.93,1:44:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧 把担架抬过来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.77,1:44:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,退到里边去
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.53,1:46:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\rEng}get out
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.46,1:46:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,出去 出去 快到街上去\N{\rEng}get out!get out!get out the street!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.60,1:46:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到街上去\N{\rEng}get out the street!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.73,1:46:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出去 德国人已经把这栋楼给包围了\N{\rEng}Get out now! The Germans have surrounded the building!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.48,1:47:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来人啊 来人啊 快来人帮我\N{\rEng}Somebody...Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.41,1:48:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 这里太脏了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.96,1:48:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我来检查这边 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.75,1:48:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细点
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.64,1:48:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-亨里齐 -我正在检查
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.85,1:48:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.48,1:48:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-快下来 -好的 这就下来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.82,1:53:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 把他们都堆在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.99,1:53:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,扔过去
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.45,1:54:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要把所有的东西都做上标记
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.46,1:54:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.71,2:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.31,2:01:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.75,2:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听懂吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.42,2:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.79,2:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.83,2:02:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.80,2:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着要把罐头打开
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.64,2:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.78,2:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里工作吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.95,2:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.35,2:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的职业是什么
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.22,2:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.23,2:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是钢琴师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.27,2:02:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,钢琴师
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.35,2:03:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.28,2:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,弹吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.67,2:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.31,2:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.75,2:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲在哪里
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.05,2:09:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,阁楼
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.32,2:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,带我去看
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.98,2:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你有吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.61,2:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,据他们所说 重要的是...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.08,2:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.51,2:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.48,2:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早安上校
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.88,2:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.23,2:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 请问...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.13,2:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那些炮火是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.70,2:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国人正要渡河
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.77,2:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需再等两个礼拜就够了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.33,2:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.70,2:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要撤退了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.41,2:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国人来了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.24,2:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.71,2:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么感谢你
Dialogue: 0,2:14:10.09,2:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝 不用谢我
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.72,2:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们死里逃生
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.86,2:14:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们要信仰他
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.90,2:14:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 拿着
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.61,2:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.74,2:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一件
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.94,2:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那件更暖和
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.28,2:14:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,战争结束后你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.65,2:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会继续在波兰电台
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.92,2:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.96,2:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.80,2:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我会来听你演奏
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.73,2:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,席皮尔曼
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.17,2:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,席皮尔曼
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.14,2:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对钢琴师来说这是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.39,2:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,德国人 德国人\N{\rEng}German! German!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.11,2:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要开枪 我是波兰人\N{\rEng}Don't shoot, I'm Polish!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.65,2:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是波兰人\N{\rEng}I'm Polish!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.19,2:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 举起双手\N{\rEng}Come out with your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:02.06,2:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我求求你\N{\rEng}Please! I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.06,2:17:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪 不要开枪 我求求你\N{\rEng}Don't shoot, don't shoot.I beg you,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.53,2:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是波兰人\N{\rEng}I'm a Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:08.83,2:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,下来\N{\rEng}Come down!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.67,2:17:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我是波兰人 拜托\N{\rEng}Please, I'm Polish.Please
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.87,2:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-拜托 -他是波兰人\N{\rEng}- Please. - He's Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.95,2:17:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 他是波兰人\N{\rEng}Yes, he's Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.38,2:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这件该死的外套是怎么回事\N{\rEng}Why the fucking coat?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.99,2:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我冷\N{\rEng}I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.24,2:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们 婊子养的德国人\N{\rEng}Look at them.German fuckers!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.74,2:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手 凶手\N{\rEng}Murderers! Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.95,2:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,肮脏的狗杂种\N{\rEng}Dirty bastards!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:01.52,2:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人魔 杂种\N{\rEng}Assassins! Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.12,2:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你们现在 你们夺走了我的一切\N{\rEng}Look at you now! You took everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:08.36,2:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个音乐家 你们夺走了我的小提琴\N{\rEng}Me, a musician.You took my violin,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:11.46,2:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们夺走我的灵魂\N{\rEng}you took my soul.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.37,2:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐家
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.47,2:18:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是音乐家
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.57,2:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}yeah
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.34,2:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你认识\N{\rEng}Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:26.71,2:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,钢琴家席皮尔曼吗
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.08,2:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他是为波兰电台演奏的
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.31,2:18:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然认识他
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.55,2:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他在避难时 我帮助过他
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.15,2:18:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我在这里
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.72,2:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请他帮助我
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.29,2:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-你叫什么名字 -霍森费尔德
Dialogue: 0,2:18:47.23,2:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.70,2:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里 我很确定\N{\rEng}It was here, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.30,2:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在已经不在了\N{\rEng}Well, it's not here now.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.67,2:20:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我对着他们咆哮\N{\rEng}I shouted, abused them.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.31,2:20:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在一点也不觉得骄傲 但我当时就是那样做的\N{\rEng}I'm not proud of it, but that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.08,2:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我当年就站在你现在这个位置\N{\rEng}I stood where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.41,2:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿围着有刺的铁丝网\N{\rEng}There was a barbed wire
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.81,2:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个德国军官向我走来\N{\rEng}and this German came up to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.32,2:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你没听到他的名字吗\N{\rEng}You didn't catch his name?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.09,2:20:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.16,2:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我去那间工厂问问 也许他们知道些什么\N{\rEng}I'll ask at the factory.They may know something.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.49,2:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（瓦列迪斯洛·席皮尔曼 继续住在华沙 直到去世）
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.76,2:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（他逝于2000年7月6日 享年88岁）
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.24,2:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,（那个德国军官的名字是威尔姆·霍森费尔德）
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.31,2:22:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（仅知他于1952年死在俄国的战俘营）
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.12,2:22:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,《钢琴家》
